  "body": "During Prater genesis our node did nothing more than validate and process AggregateAndProof from gossip. Download and inspect the profile below.\r\n\r\n- Our node should have some queue to prevent being DDOS by gossip messages.\r\n- How should this queue be designed?\r\n- Should we prioritize some messages (blocks) over others (attestations)?\r\n\r\n[lodestar-64vali-pratergenesis-CPU-20210323T092838.cpuprofile.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/6196079/lodestar-64vali-pratergenesis-CPU-20210323T092838.cpuprofile.zip)\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\nBetween `2021-03-23 15:14:19` and `2021-03-23 15:15:41` our Beacon node on Prater validated 487 AggregateAndProof and did nothing else.\r\n",
